                    <span>This book is simple and concise. There are four things to be conscious of and  practice. If you are looking for an uncomplicated way to practice spirituality, this may be the one for you.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Could have been a pamphlet</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
